{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_122","type":"agent_message","text":"Added exact `4.2.1.Final` metadata mappings for Netty core modules and new minimal version directories under `metadata/io.netty` so `netty-transport:4.2.1.Final` no longer falls back to older `4.1.x` repo metadata. The main changes are in [metadata/io.netty/netty-transport/index.json](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/metadata/io.netty/netty-transport/index.json), [metadata/io.netty/netty-common/index.json](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/metadata/io.netty/netty-common/index.json), [metadata/io.netty/netty-buffer/index.json](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/metadata/io.netty/netty-buffer/index.json), [metadata/io.netty/netty-codec-http/index.json](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/metadata/io.netty/netty-codec-http/index.json), and [metadata/io.netty/netty-handler/index.json](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/metadata/io.netty/netty-handler/index.json), plus the new `4.2.1.Final/reachability-metadata.json` files.\n\nThe actual Java 25 native-image failure was a Netty runtime-state issue, so I also updated [tests/src/io.netty/netty-transport/4.1.115.Final/build.gradle](/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/919-d11128c9/tests/src/io.netty/netty-transport/4.1.115.Final/build.gradle) to:\n- force the allocator/`PlatformDependent` classes to initialize at runtime for the native test image\n- run the native test with `-Dio.netty.noUnsafe=false` and `-Dio.netty.maxDirectMemory=1048576`\n\nVerified with `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates